  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "スーパーマリオコレクションは、スーパーファミコン向けに発売された、任天堂のマリオをフィーチャーしたすべてのプラットフォームゲームのコンピレーションです。内容には、スーパーマリオブラザーズ1、2、3、そしてこれまでヨーロッパでは未発売だったスーパーマリオブラザーズ：ザ・ロストレベルズが含まれています。単なるコンピレーションにとどまらず、ゲームはグラフィックの向上と進行状況を保存する機能を提供します。初代任天堂のファンには懐かしさを感じさせる作品です。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Super Mario All-Stars is a compilation of remasters for the Super Nintendo Entertainment System. It enhances Super Mario Bros., Super Mario Bros. 2, Super Mario Bros. 3 and Super Mario Bros.: The Lost Levels with an added on-cartridge save feature, updated graphics and sound, and an additional \"battle game\" for Super Mario Bros. 3. It is also the first time that the original Japanese Super Mario Bros. 2 was released for the western public.\n\nRevisit the magic and fun of the classic Super Mario Bros. series on your Super NES! All the great Super Mario Bros. games for the NES have been powered up with 16-bit graphics and sound and collected on one super game pak. As an added bonus, the previously unreleased \"Lost Levels\" are included. These super challenging courses have never been available in this country until now!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Each of the 4 games in the set contain their own stories",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
